[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scripts/game/socket_power_repair.gd" id="3_repair"]

; A ship system whose ONLY fix is a power feed — no patch panel. It breaks like any malfunction
; (RunState finds it via the "malfunctions" group), but the only way back is to plug a live cable
; into its inlet: run one the long way from a wall outlet, or charge the battery and carry it here.
; The console has an inlet socket on its +Z face and a status light (red broken / green fixed).
; Place it well away from any source outlet — that "no socket in reach" is the whole point.

